This package bundles tokenizer assets derived from official Hugging Face repositories under the mistralai organization:
- mistralai/Devstral-Small-2-24B-Instruct-2512 tokenizer.json
- mistralai/Devstral-Small-2505 tekken.json
- mistralai/Leanstral-2603 tekken.json
- mistralai/Mathstral-7B-v0.1 tokenizer.json
- mistralai/Mamba-Codestral-7B-v0.1 tokenizer.json
- mistralai/Magistral-Small-2507 tekken.json
- mistralai/Ministral-3-3B-Base-2512 tokenizer.json
- mistralai/Mistral-7B-v0.1 tokenizer.json
- mistralai/Mistral-7B-v0.3 tokenizer.json
- mistralai/Mistral-Nemo-Base-2407 tokenizer.json
- mistralai/Mistral-Small-3.2-24B-Instruct-2506 tekken.json
- mistralai/Mistral-Small-24B-Base-2501 tokenizer.json
- mistralai/Mixtral-8x7B-v0.1 tokenizer.json

For families derived from official `tekken.json`, the published payload is a converted `tokenizer.json` representation produced to match the official `mistral-common` tokenizer behavior.

